xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104ndv1719414830445.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ndv1719414830445.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/ndv1719414830445.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"txq1665702760369\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $subsetreturn\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"txq1665702760369___subsetreturn_291174\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return only the most recently retrieved occurrences of an entity to its operation entity parameter.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"txq1665702760369__topic_d89888e1_d89889e1_d89890e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"txq1665702760369__p_d89891e1_d89892e1_d89893e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$subsetreturn</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"txq1665702760369__p_d89894e1_d89895e1_d89896e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$subsetreturn</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Expression</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"txq1665702760369__p_d89897e1_d89898e1_d89899e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">set</span> | <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">reset</span>\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$subsetreturn</span>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"txq1665702760369__topic_d59812e1_d59813e1_d59814e1_d59815e1_d59816e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d297482e119\">\n                       \n Parameters\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"txq1665702760369__d6157e20\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Parameters</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"txq1665702760369__d6157e20__entry__1\">\n Parameter\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"txq1665702760369__d6157e20__entry__2\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"txq1665702760369__d6157e20__entry__3\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txq1665702760369__d6157e20__entry__1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txq1665702760369__d6157e20__entry__2\">\n String\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txq1665702760369__d6157e20__entry__3\">\n Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"txq1665702760369__topic_d59817e1_d59818e1_d59819e1_d59820e1_d59821e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d297482e173\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"txq1665702760369__table_d9752e1_d9753e1_d9754e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 2. </span><span class=\"title\">Return Values</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"txq1665702760369__table_d9752e1_d9753e1_d9754e1__entry__1\">\n Data Type\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"txq1665702760369__table_d9752e1_d9753e1_d9754e1__entry__2\">\n Meaning\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txq1665702760369__table_d9752e1_d9753e1_d9754e1__entry__1\">\n Numeric\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txq1665702760369__table_d9752e1_d9753e1_d9754e1__entry__2\">Number of most recently retrieved occurrences\n                        of an entity to its operation entity parameter. If\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$subsetreturn</span> is not enabled <code class=\"ph codeph\">0</code> is\n                        returned. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"txq1665702760369__p_d89906e1_d89907e1_d89908e1\">If an error occurs, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> contains a negative value that identifies the exact error.</p>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"3\" id=\"txq1665702760369__table_d9755e1_d9756e1_d9757e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 3. </span><span class=\"title\">Values of <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$procerror</span> Commonly Returned Following\n                  <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$subsetreturn</span>\n</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"txq1665702760369__table_d9755e1_d9756e1_d9757e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Value</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"txq1665702760369__table_d9755e1_d9756e1_d9757e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Error constant</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"txq1665702760369__table_d9755e1_d9756e1_d9757e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Meaning</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txq1665702760369__table_d9755e1_d9756e1_d9757e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">-1102</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txq1665702760369__table_d9755e1_d9756e1_d9757e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">&lt;UPROCERR_ENTITY&gt;</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txq1665702760369__table_d9755e1_d9756e1_d9757e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txq1665702760369__table_d9755e1_d9756e1_d9757e1__entry__1\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">-1113</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txq1665702760369__table_d9755e1_d9756e1_d9757e1__entry__2\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">&lt;UPROCERR_PARAMETER&gt;</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"txq1665702760369__table_d9755e1_d9756e1_d9757e1__entry__3\" rowspan=\"1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Parameter name not valid or not defined.</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"txq1665702760369__topic_d59822e1_d59823e1_d59824e1_d59825e1_d59826e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d297482e318\">\n                       \n Use\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"txq1665702760369__p_d89912e1_d89913e1_d89914e1\">Use in Form, Report, and Service components.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"txq1665702760369__p_d89915e1_d89916e1_d89917e1\">Allowed in an operation with an entity parameter, <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>, whose direction is OUT or INOUT.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"txq1665702760369__topic_d59827e1_d59828e1_d59829e1_d59830e1_d59831e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d297482e334\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"txq1665702760369__p_d89921e1_d89922e1_d89923e1\">An entity parameter usually contains all occurrences of that entity. However, <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$subsetreturn</span> provides the entity parameter with only the most recently retrieved occurrences of <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>. This is especially useful for, but not limited to, retrieving with <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">retrieve/a</span>. Occurrences that are removed from the hitlist, or deleted from the database are not returned.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"txq1665702760369__section_vp4_wbj_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d297482e352\">Example: Return a Hitlist Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$subsetreturn</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">In this example <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$subsetreturn</span> is used to return a\n               hitlist that includes all customers from the USA:</p>\n<p class=\"p\">So where's the retrieve profile to get only USA customers?</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"txq1665702760369__pre_ffb_xbj_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">operation GET_USA_CUSTOMERS\nparams\n entity CUSTOMER : OUT\nendparams\ncreocc \"CUSTOMER\", 0\nretrieve/a \"CUSTOMER\"\nset $subsetreturn\nend ; GET_USA_CUSTOMERS\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qbv1665702599441.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>retrieve/a</a><p>Retrieve multiple additional occurrences of the specified entity without discarding the hitlist.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/eww1719683180873.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>set</a><p>Set the value of the specified ProcScript function to 1 (TRUE).</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ukk1665702596834.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>reset</a><p>Reset the value of the specified ProcScript function to 0.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7422433\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_7422433\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$subsetreturn Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $subsetreturn Return only the most recently retrieved occurrences of an entity to its operation entity parameter. $subsetreturn ( Entity ) $subsetreturn ( Entity ) = Expression set | reset $subsetreturn ( Entity ) Parameters Table 1. Parameters Parameter Data Type Description Entity String Entity name. If omitted, the current entity is used. Return Values Table 2. Return Values Data Type Meaning Numeric Number of most recently retrieved occurrences of an entity to its operation entity parameter. If $subsetreturn is not enabled 0 is returned. If an error occurs, $procerror contains a negative value that identifies the exact error. Table 3. Values of $procerror Commonly Returned Following $subsetreturn Value Error constant Meaning -1102 <UPROCERR_ENTITY> The entity name provided is not a valid name or the entity is not painted on the component. -1113 <UPROCERR_PARAMETER> Parameter name not valid or not defined. Use Use in Form, Report, and Service components. Allowed in an operation with an entity parameter, Entity , whose direction is OUT or INOUT. Description An entity parameter usually contains all occurrences of that entity. However, $subsetreturn provides the entity parameter with only the most recently retrieved occurrences of Entity . This is especially useful for, but not limited to, retrieving with retrieve/a . Occurrences that are removed from the hitlist, or deleted from the database are not returned. Example: Return a Hitlist Using $subsetreturn In this example $subsetreturn is used to return a hitlist that includes all customers from the USA: So where's the retrieve profile to get only USA customers? operation GET_USA_CUSTOMERS params entity CUSTOMER : OUT endparams creocc \"CUSTOMER\", 0 retrieve/a \"CUSTOMER\" set $subsetreturn end ; GET_USA_CUSTOMERS Copy Related Links retrieve/a Retrieve multiple additional occurrences of the specified entity without discarding the hitlist. set Set the value of the specified ProcScript function to 1 (TRUE). reset Reset the value of the specified ProcScript function to 0. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}